WEBVTT

00:01.067 --> 00:03.406
Previously on "mistresses"...

00:04.235 --> 00:06.538
Thomas said that's why you
gave him the prescription...

00:06.538 --> 00:08.606
For when things got too painful.

00:08.606 --> 00:11.943
How would you describe the
mental state of your patient

00:11.943 --> 00:13.411
in the weeks leading up to his death?

00:13.411 --> 00:15.513
You think that I let
Sally walk all over me,

00:15.513 --> 00:16.715
and you know what? You're right.

00:16.715 --> 00:18.283
You're a good friend, Joss.

00:18.283 --> 00:19.784
Six months ago, I lost my job,

00:19.784 --> 00:21.319
but this isn't about me anymore.

00:21.319 --> 00:22.320
It's about Scottie.

00:22.320 --> 00:23.488
He needs your help.

00:23.488 --> 00:25.657
There's a recently developed paternity test

00:25.657 --> 00:28.493
that only requires a D.N.A.
sample from the mother

00:28.493 --> 00:30.395
and potential father.

