♪ you prayed to have your name
scattered on the lips of the young ♪

00:48.057 --> 00:52.900
♪ now you claim that it's you
on the tips of the tongue ♪

00:52.990 --> 00:57.676
♪ and if you're proud of what you
had to kill to get your thrill ♪

00:57.681 --> 01:01.537
♪ well, I bet it stings
to give up everything ♪

01:01.538 --> 01:04.640
♪ and realize that they don't want you ♪

01:04.650 --> 01:09.740
♪ it's a lonely road
where the forgotten go ♪

01:09.741 --> 01:13.423
♪ where your misery finds it company ♪

01:14.961 --> 01:20.049
♪ it's a long way down
to the sacred ground ♪

01:20.050 --> 01:25.435
