38:53.406 --> 38:55.074
♪ ba, ba-da ♪

38:55.074 --> 38:57.143
♪ ah, ah ♪

38:57.143 --> 39:01.981
♪ standing by your side ♪

39:01.981 --> 39:04.651
♪ ah, ah ♪

39:04.651 --> 39:07.053
♪ I will be there ♪

39:07.053 --> 39:08.988
♪ ah, ah ♪
♪ ba, ba-da ♪

39:08.988 --> 39:10.590
♪ ah, ah ♪

39:10.590 --> 39:14.294
♪ ba, ba-da ♪
♪ standing by your side ♪

39:14.294 --> 39:16.696
♪ ba, ba-da ♪

39:16.696 --> 39:22.631
(characters on TV speaking indistinctly)

39:24.440 --> 39:26.408
(Chuckles) Watch this next part.

39:26.408 --> 39:29.356
"Wait a second."

39:29.356 --> 39:30.690
"Just kidding"?

39:30.690 --> 39:32.982
(Laughs) Mm.

39:33.172 --> 39:36.421
I'm taking a shower. Care to join me?

39:36.421 --> 39:39.491
No, thanks. Do you mind if
I change the channel, though?

39:39.491 --> 39:41.493
Yeah. Sure. Just make sure you record it.

39:41.493 --> 39:43.461
It's an awesome ep.

39:43.461 --> 39:45.997
Okay. (Chuckles)

39:45.997 --> 39:47.265
(Speaks indistinctly)

39:47.265 --> 39:49.434
Or a...

39:50.969 --> 39:53.206
(Cell phone alert chirps)

39:54.956 --> 39:56.941
__. A lizard?

39:56.941 --> 39:58.343
(Chuckles)

39:58.344 --> 40:01.644
(Gossip's "Into the wild" playing)

40:04.125 --> 40:07.944
__

40:08.520 --> 40:09.988
(Cell phone alert chirps)

40:09.988 --> 40:12.317
(Laughs)

40:12.318 --> 40:15.142
__

40:15.126 --> 40:19.126
♪ tell you all the words you want to hear ♪

40:20.031 --> 40:21.866
(cell phone rings)

40:21.866 --> 40:23.234
♪ so I went... ♪

40:23.234 --> 40:24.769
Hey.

40:24.769 --> 40:27.405
- Hey. What are you doing right now?
- Nothing, really.

40:27.405 --> 40:28.873
Yeah.

40:28.873 --> 40:30.408
No. I'm coming over.

40:30.408 --> 40:32.444
I gotta meet the new roommate.

40:32.444 --> 40:35.146
♪ in the wild ♪

40:35.146 --> 40:37.082
♪ to the wild ♪

40:37.082 --> 40:39.350
Hey, we totally use the same conditioner.

40:39.350 --> 40:42.554
Really... odd.

40:42.554 --> 40:44.322
Joss?

40:44.322 --> 40:46.357
♪ in the wild ♪

40:46.357 --> 40:49.427
♪ to the wild ♪

40:49.427 --> 40:52.330
(Richard and April laugh)

40:52.330 --> 40:54.766
♪ it's all over now ♪

40:54.766 --> 40:56.234
(sighs)

40:56.234 --> 40:57.235
(Sighs)

40:57.235 --> 40:57.963
Oh, my God.

40:57.963 --> 40:59.214
You're gonna have to mark down this bed

40:59.214 --> 41:01.850
- after what we just put it through.
- (Laughs)

41:01.850 --> 41:03.552
Oh, God. Who am I?

41:03.552 --> 41:07.389
You are a reckless, irresponsible,

41:07.389 --> 41:09.257
linen-selling goddess.

41:09.257 --> 41:12.360
That was amazing.

41:12.360 --> 41:14.763
Was that amazing or has
it just been too long?

41:14.763 --> 41:16.932
No. That was amazing.

41:16.932 --> 41:17.999
That was the one to beat.

41:17.999 --> 41:19.267
Mm.

41:19.267 --> 41:22.971
♪ ... Cities over islands ♪

41:22.971 --> 41:24.806
♪ I'm returning to the place... ♪

41:24.806 --> 41:26.608
Richard?

41:26.608 --> 41:27.909
Yeah?

41:27.909 --> 41:29.844
Oh, my God.

41:29.844 --> 41:30.779
What? What time is it?

41:30.779 --> 41:32.347
Oh, the kids!

41:32.347 --> 41:33.682
Oh! Totally lost track of time.

41:33.682 --> 41:35.917
I know! So did I... w... where's my... oh.

41:35.917 --> 41:37.986
Here. Sorry.

41:37.986 --> 41:39.554
- Wait a minute.
- What?

41:39.554 --> 41:42.324
Lucy's at play rehearsal.

41:42.324 --> 41:44.826
Madi's with her grandma.

41:44.826 --> 41:46.962
(Belt rattles) (Giggles)

41:46.962 --> 41:50.932
(Laughs)

42:07.249 --> 42:09.718
(Chuckles)

42:09.718 --> 42:11.219
(Clears throat)

42:11.219 --> 42:12.454
Oops.

42:12.454 --> 42:13.755
I guess you were right.

42:13.755 --> 42:16.791
I was kind of getting my hopes up.

42:16.791 --> 42:18.460
You know what?

42:19.894 --> 42:21.930
It'll come in handy one day.

42:26.301 --> 42:27.802
Babe, what's wrong?

42:33.675 --> 42:35.810
I'm pregnant, Harry...

42:37.712 --> 42:40.849
but it might not be yours.

